column1: # Description: parameters used in flexitarian's diet computation
# s: 'scale' binom. param (fixed) --> models the slope of the curve (if bigger; softer)
# t0: 'location' binom. param --> models peak year where more people will become flexetarian
# wf: flexetarians' weight --> models the social pressure of the flexitarians' group
# k: percentage of flexitarian population by 2100; value computed based on wf; k_m; k_M; and k_sigma
